  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgeModel
    Basic POJO for storing user age and data.
    BaseResponse
    Base response when we only need a simple callback from RESTful API.
    CompleteIdentificationModel
    Model containing all information about a user.
    DeviceMessage
    Used to prepare the payload for a Nearby Message.
    FlarePojo
    Basic POJO used to contain information about user location for "Flare" feature.
    LoginPojo
    Simple POJO used for getting user login data and passing it as JSON.
    Match
    Basic POJO containing information about matches to other users in the database.
    RegisterPojo  
    UserId

    UserModel

    UserPojo

    UserToken
    Simple POJO containing a token required for most user action.
